Package: semanticscholar
Type: Package
Title: Data From Semantic Scholar Leightweight API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Markus",
           family = "Skyttner",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "markussk@kth.se")
Description: Semantic Scholar is a free, AI-powered research tool for scientific
    literature available at https://semanticscholar.org. It provides a RESTful 
    API for convenient linking to Semantic Scholar pages and pulling information 
    about individual records on demand. This R package wraps the lightweight API 
    in order to facilitate on demand access to records in this data source.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
